data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath brick home located in desirable community of Hearthstone built by Trusst Builders.  The main level offers large kitchen, dining room and living room with coffered ceiling along with master suite and two guest bedrooms.  Hardwood floors thru out the 1st floor including bedrooms, tile in all bathrooms.  All counter tops are granite including bathrooms.  Master bath has large tile shower.  Large screened in porch and custom planation blinds thru out the home.Community Pool
